							　　作者：iamtaiwanese4  回覆日期：2010-5-13 21:09:00　　Murky area　　　　　　　　China already has experience in regulating cutting-edge technologies by assessing clinical trials and conducting ethical reviews. It was the first country to give governmental approval for a gene-therapy treatment, one produced by SiBiono GeneTech in Shenzhen that targets head and neck cancers.　　___________________________________________________________________　　那麼愛裝牛逼，請問：  （限制當天回答，別隔天帶去問你的英文老師）　　　　I suggested that the plan _____.　　(1)should not give up  (2)not be given up　　(3)should give up      (4)be not given up　　　　I shall go on working late today _____tomorrow.　　(1)for the purpose of freedom  (2)so as to free　　(3)so as to be free            (4)lest I am free
							
							
						

